query:
SELECT 
  rw.id, 
  rw.contactName, 
  rw.contactLabels, 
  rw.stopColor,
  (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(CONCAT(labelName, ':', color) SEPARATOR '; ') 
   FROM label_colors 
   WHERE userId = r.userId) as user_label_colors
FROM route_waypoints rw
JOIN routes r ON rw.routeId = r.id
WHERE rw.routeId = 1860004 
ORDER BY rw.position 
LIMIT 3
